sources.title: Comeback Season | Full Romantic Comedy | Ray Liotta | Shaun Sipos
sources.description:
Comeback Season - A comedy about a cheating husband (Ray Liotta) and an injured high school football star (Shaun Sipos) who become court ordered roommates. Emotional carnage leads to unlikely alliances, as the two men scramble for a second chance at love and stardom.
2006.  Stars: Ray Liotta, Shaun Sipos, Glenne Headly, Rachel Blanchard
